Devyani Shorey( Namrata Bidasaria6 episodes, 2020 ). Taaruk Raina( Anmol Malhotra6 episodes, 2020 ). Vihaan Samat( Harsh Agarwal6 episodes, 2020 ). Rannvijay Singh( Siddharth Sinha6 episodes, 2020 ). Vidya Malvade( Zeenath Karim / …6 episodes, 2020 ). Kritika Bharadwaj( Simran Malhotra6 episodes, 2020 ). Abhinav Sharma( Krish Katyal6 episodes, 2020 ). Imran Rasheed( Kaku6 episodes, 2020 ). Ruturaj Shinde( Momo6 episodes, 2020 ). Sarthak Kakar( Lover Boy6 episodes, 2020 ). Abhinay Raj Singh( Abhi6 episodes, 2020 ). Gurii( Gur6 episodes, 2020 ). Buddhdev Yash( Danish Tamang6 episodes, 2020 ). Priya Banerjee( Ayesha Duggirala6 episodes, 2022 ). Hitesh Rathod Viratian( Raghavv3 episodes, 2020 ). Suhasini Mulay( Rishi’s Dadi Ma2 episodes, 2020 ). Kshitee Jog( Simple Ahuja2 episodes, 2020 ). Jatin Sial( Dheeraj Ahuja2 episodes, 2020 ). Pradeep Rajput( Raghav2 episodes, 2020 ). Bikram Malati( Bikram / …2 episodes, 2020 ). Aditi Govitrikar( Kalpana1 episode, 2020 ). Sartaaj Kakkar( Rishi singh1 episode, 2020 ). Kiran Dorad(1 episode, 2020 ). Paras Gola(1 episode, 2020 ). Vaibhav Palhade( Samar1 episode, 2020 ). Abhishek Andrews( Abhishek Andrews1 episode ). Trishna Singh( Shahana (2020)unknown episodes ). Ravin Makhija( (2020)unknown episodes)

Language Hindi

Producers Pashan Jal. Salona Bains Joshi. Sonia Kanwar. Radhika Loya. Sanjeevkumar Nair. Lohita Phooken. Ronnie Screwvala. Sanaya Irani Zohrabi. Amish Shah
